Rob is an avid gamer. He's also a very funny and creative guy.

10
00:00:31,991 --> 00:00:34,212
And he loves the apocalypse, of course.

11
00:00:34,212 --> 00:00:35,572
So his favorite game is Fallout 3.

12
00:00:35,572 --> 00:00:37,752
This is his Fallout 3 character.

13
00:00:37,752 --> 00:00:39,533
But most of the time, his character

14
00:00:39,533 --> 00:00:40,733
doesn't look like this.

15
00:00:40,733 --> 00:00:41,753
Because if you know Fallout 3, you

16
00:00:41,753 --> 00:00:43,874
know that you can have different pieces of equipment,

17
00:00:43,874 --> 00:00:46,394
like a helmet that might give you a special ability

18
00:00:46,394 --> 00:00:48,495
or extra protection or something.

19
00:00:48,495 --> 00:00:50,535
But it also changes the way you look.

20
